      "description": "Well-kept good-condition car that presents nicely and appears complete, usable, and ready to enjoy as a solid driver. Paint, trim, and interior show normal age and use, with some minor cosmetic flaws you\u2019d expect from a car that has been driven and cared for rather than fully restored. Overall, it looks honest and tidy, and should suit a buyer looking for a dependable, presentable classic they can use and improve over time if desired.",
