      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Priced to move, this vehicle offers a straightforward, budget-friendly way into dependable transportation. It shows its age cosmetically and is best suited for a buyer who values affordability, practicality, and strong potential as a daily driver, starter car, or light project. A solid opportunity to own at a very accessible price.",
