    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly car with plenty of life left for the right person? This one isn\u2019t perfect and shows its age, but it\u2019s an honest little vehicle that could make a great starter, backup car, or project for someone handy. A practical option if you want affordable wheels without spending a fortune. Priced to sell and ready for its next chapter.",
