      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A true diamond-in-the-rough with loads of personality, this car has the kind of honest, road-worn character that makes it feel like a faithful old companion. It\u2019s the perfect choice for someone who sees potential where others just see age\u2014a practical, budget-friendly ride for getting around town, tackling a project, or keeping as a handy extra vehicle. If you appreciate a machine with a story and don\u2019t mind giving it a little love, this one offers an affordable way into ownership with plenty of spirit left to share.",
